<item>
            <title>[PIG-2128] Generating the jar file takes a lot of time and is unnecessary when running Pig local mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2128</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since the Pig local mode implementation has been moved to Hadoop local it is very slow.&lt;br/&gt;
We should optimize some of the steps so that it is more user friendly.&lt;br/&gt;
In this case we should skip building the jar for each job as it runs in the same process.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
